cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software or methodology in research, please cite it as below."
title: "Magistra Predictor: A Dual-Track Framework for GLP-1 Side Effect Estimation"
abstract: "An open, continuously updated system that estimates GLP-1 medication side effect risk by reporting two parallel estimates per effect: clinical trial evidence and real-world patient reports, displayed side by side without blending. Implements DerSimonian-Laird random-effects confidence intervals, FDR-corrected empirical modifier estimation, and a self-evolving parameter update pipeline with safety guardrails."
